        "reaction_type": "加氢反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在间歇反应器中，使用Raney Ni催化剂，在50°C、1.0-5.0 MPa氢气压力和甲醇溶剂条件下，对二糠叉丙酮（F2A）进行低温加氢，将其转化为氢化二糠叉丙酮二聚体（H-F2A）。",
        "text_snippet": "the first step of F2A hydrogenation was carried out in the same batch reactor of 140 mL at 50°C, 1.0–5.0 MPa and 800 rpm stirring with Raney Ni catalyst. In each run, 8.0 g of F2A, 2.0 g of Raney Ni and 32 ml solvent (methanol, THF or cyclohexane) were charged in the batch reactor.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在固定床反应器中，使用1wt% Pt/SiO2-ZrO2催化剂，在260-320°C、60 ml/min氢气条件下，对第一步加氢产生的H-F2A甲醇溶液进行高温加氢脱氧（HDO），将其转化为C8-C14液态烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "the second step of HDO of the hydrogenated H-F2A dimers to liquid alkanes in a fixed-bed reactor... at 260–320°C. The liquid hourly space velocity (LHSV) of H-F2A solution and H2 flow rate was 0.75 h−1 and 60 ml/min respectively.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
